# ============================================================================
# Muffin Toolchain — ar.rsp.tmpl (MAX)
# Path: /docs/examples/rsp/ar.rsp.tmpl
#
# Purpose:
# - Response-file template for an "ar" invocation (static archive builder).
# - Avoids command line length limits (esp. on Windows).
#
# Template language (doc-oriented):
# - {out}              => output archive path
# - {inputs}           => list of input object files (one per line)
# - {flags}            => tool flags (optional, one per line or space-separated)
# - {cwd}              => working directory (optional)
# - {extra}            => extra args (optional)
#
# Recommended usage (from MUF):
#   run tool "ar"
#     args add "@{toolchain_assets}/response_files/ar.rsp"
#   .end
# - Or your driver expands this template into a real .rsp file in cache dir.
# ============================================================================

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Common ar mode: "rcs" (replace/insert, create, write index)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
rcs
{out}

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional flags (expanded by Muffin if provided)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
{flags}

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Inputs (one per line is the most portable across ar variants)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
{inputs}

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Extra arguments (rare)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
{extra}
